  QL_FironeMini_TerribleThunder_Desc:
    contents:
      - text: "西米纳总是愁眉不展，\n心烦的原因好像是"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 雷
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n\n不知道为什么"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 雷
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "经常会落在湖畔驿站。\n她拜托你去调查其中原因。"
  QL_FironeMini_TerribleThunder_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "听了你的报告之后，\n西米纳也放下心来。\n但她好像还是害怕雷声。"
  QL_FironeMini_TerribleThunder_Name:
    contents:
      - text: 害怕打雷
  QL_FironeMini_TerribleThunder_Remove:
    contents:
      - text: "湖畔驿站的最高处插着一把金属制的武器。\n大概是因为这把武器，驿站才容易落"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 雷
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n\n把这件事告诉西米纳，让她放心吧。"
